stories.text: Not sure how much effort i want to put into this, as i’ve already wasted enough time on it, though it might be interesting to web sleuths. Basically, i’m not sure reddit was ever a quality site, but it appears to me it’s been getting crumbier and crumbier with funny tokens and power ups and by my observation poor moderation. TLDR i got banned from the buttcoin sub for exhibiting common behavior, and now i’m getting the runaround. It wouldn’t bother me except that there are no good alternatives to reddit. Anyway, here’s the link: https://www.reddit.com/r/WatchRedditDie/comments/t30iej/comment/hys6a0k/
